Here a global phase of $-\pi/2$ has been added.
In this experiment, $\Omega$, $\phi$ and $\omega$ can be changed to control the amplitude of the force term $f(t)\hat{x}$, realize the momentum term $h(t)\hat{p}$ and vary the nominal trap frequency.
